description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Sagrada Família（Works of Antoni Gaudí）
-Dolomites
-Yellowstone National Park
-Colosseum (Historic district of Rome)
-Piazza dei Miracoli
-Old City of Dubrovnik
-Memphis and its Necropolis
-Amalfi Coast
-Göreme Historical National Park
-Great Wall of China
name: World Heritage Site 3
